<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>٥٠] هَلْ أُنَبِّئُكُمْ <span class="c4">[المائدة: ٦٠]</span>.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
